1. Rats also have feelings
A rat or a cockroach runs away when they feel the danger. Does that mean that they also feel the fear?
Neuroscientist Joseph Le Doux is convinced of this: many animals also have feelings.
4. But how could it be verified if, when they behave in the same way as we do, they have the same feelings as we do?
