Heinz-Christian Strache, to the left of the Austrian right wing of the Freedom Party and Filip Dewinter of the Belgian right-wing Vlaams Belang party, take part in a demonstration to present the organization "City against Islamization" in Antwerp, on Thursday 17 January 2008.
They carry road signs like those representing mosques with a red line passing in the middle.
