A spokesman for the local Islamic community said they were "deeply shocked" by the news of the desecration, which occurred towards the end of Ramadan, a month of religious significance for Muslims.
Austria has meanwhile embarked on a journey of spiritual research following its turn to the right in yesterday’s parliamentary elections.
